io.smudgr.util

Class SmudgrJar

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.smudgr.util.SmudgrJar

  • public class SmudgrJar
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a jar file and the resources within it.

    This is used to enumerate classes for reflection, or load UI files from a build.
